        "action": "Freeze Rent / Mortgage payments for poorly people who are not be fit to work.",
        "additional_details": "Help sick people to stay in their homes by covering their rent payments in full through benefits or if they have a mortgage then freeze their payments until they are fit to return to work.",
        "background": "People are getting evicted from their homes due to not being able to afford their rent / mortgage payments when they have a serious illness such as cancer. Sometimes benefits won't cover the mortgage / rent payments.",
